values:
So, I haven't written on this blog in a while......I've started a new one             

http://drbarbie09.blogspot.com/       

 for anyone who wishes to read about my life......

I've enjoyed this blog, its definitely given me a good outlet for the highs and lows of the past 3 years.....and now its time for the new one...yay

Fools rush in
Where angels fear to tread
And so I come to you my love
My heart above my head

Though I see
The danger there
If there's a chance for me
Then I don't care

Fools rush in
Where wise men never go
But wise men never fall in love
So how are they to know?

When we met
I felt my life begin
So open up your heart and let
This fool rush in

Oh, open up your heart and let
This fool rush in

Whoa open up your heart and let
This fool rush in

so me nd my friends went to this new restaurant/bar called ketchup at the national harbor....its this posh place, they have one in LA

i liked it...its a little over pricey...but the harbor was absolutely beautiful, and the weather was perfect...im really enjoying the small pleasures in life

from time to time, things stress me out, but the key to living a happy & healthy life is to take the time to enjoy things around you

so im gna try :)
so like, i have a boyfriend now...how odd
" I'm wishing that someday, you'll miss me terribly that no matter how hard you'll look for me, you wouldn't find me...because I want you to miss me the same way I'm missing you." - unknown

hmmm i havent really been posting much lately...i guess there isnt a whole lot to say

ive just been working..sleeping..and occasionally going out

recently i told one of my guys that i just didnt see it workin out with us...and its weird cause now im so used to him callin/textin all the time...and now i sorta miss it

but i told him to stop cause i didnt think i liked him that much...now im wondering if i made a mistake

its weird cause when i end it with someone usually i never look back

but now im lookin back and its only been like 2 days

hmmm...anyway he said he still wants to hang out tmrw...so we shall see

on another note...im trying to get my loans for school...so hopefully everything will work out with that and my move to miami will be a smooth transition...its crazy cause i wont be working for the next 4 yrs....just studying all day/everyday...how odd cause ive always held a job since i turned 16

and its gna be really intense...ive received the syllabus for all of the classes and im already intimidated...i really am looking forward to microbio and immunology and even the dr/patient/society course....but im reallllly scared about anatomy, histology, biochem, and physio...eeeks!

i guess im kinda nervous cause my background is english...i took all the pre-reqs for med school with all the chem/bio classes....but the majority of the classes i took in college were related to literature and writing...this is certainly going to be a steep hill to climb..

i think that its true what they say...

when one area of your life is going well, the other falls spectacularly to pieces...

i got in an argument with one of my aunts...my dads family is always criticizing me about not calling enough/spending enough time with the fam...and im seriously sick of it.

i admit that im not a big phone person...but i do the best i can....i dont take criticism very well so i need a little time to cool off..

ick...but moving along...i just feel so emotionally jaded..

i should feel incredibly lucky cause my new guy jonny is so sweet & amazing...but its like overshadowed by how awful my past guy has been treating me..

im just always hurt by him, and i dont kno why i go back for more

i must be a masochist or something...like drawn to painful relationships...i dont even understand it

i think that i need to learn to let go...ive never had such a hard time getting over someone...i just wonder why me?

this is supposed to be a happy time in my life...im really excited about my future..and i just need to move forward

i do eventually want to be in a happy & successful relationship and eventually marriage..so i need to see guys for what they really are...bad boys really are bad and WONT change..i dont need that in my life anymore.

God is so good to me...I need to pray more..

I got into another school! yay! well technically its a medprep first but a guaranteed spot tho...the first semester is in miami, before taking off for the islands for 2 yrs and the last 2 yrs in clinicals in the US.  It would definitely be a world tour but one well worth it I hope!

I need to make a decision soon b/c I only have 2 weeks before I have to pay the hefty deposit.  EEeeeks...I read the syllabus and Im not gonna lie im very intimidated.  The class structure is serious.  I mean I know its med school and all but the rules are kinda strict.  Attendance is obviously mandatory, tardiness is forbidden, and dont even think about trying to wear jeans to class.  And lets not get started on the content of the classes...it looks like the professors move at lightning speed.  I just hope I can keep up *fingers crossed*

But changing the subject...if i can take off from work, I can go with my dad to Boston for the july 4th weekend yayyy!

...so we shall see...

today has been a very good day...thank you God!
I GOT INTO MEDICAL SCHOOL!!!! I cant believe it!! im in a state of euphoria...words cant describe

im in a love/hate relationship with my scale...

this past yr ive lost some weight due to my lack of excessive drinking...and i got sick a few times...prob from my patients...so i lost like 19-20 lbs...give or take a few


but now im like putting the weight back on... YUCK

im annoyed...its prob cause all i do these days is work work work then stuff my face when i get home....im so terrible about sticking to any kind of exercise regimen...but i realllllly need to

1.) Become an MD
2.) Move to California
3.) See the world
4.) Move into big house w/ a white picket fence
5.) Raise 2.5 children
6.) Retire at age 50


Well...I already have a retirement account. LOL :)

I have a med school interview via telephone on tuesday morning, and another school interview on June 9th in Charlotte, North Carolina......


Im SO nervous.

Im so unprepared.


The process to becoming a practicing physician in this country is a long and tumultuous one. 

Oyyy vey

im gonna start acting like a guy.

forget feelings, fuck emotions..

from now on, i dont care anymore...im just gonna go back to hookups...cause at least i know those rules.

its over..i finally got the answer that i wanted


i asked him point blank if he was in love with me...and he said no


thats all i needed to know


my heart is broken in a million pieces


i dont want to date anyone for a while.


now i just need to work on me.

i had a great time at umass...i got the reunion with my friends...and my lover lol 


i already miss him, he says he already misses me...but thats life...i truly do think however that i have fallen in love with him, i wish i could find the right words to express it to him

so im posting this from umass...i cant believe i actually made it here, on a whim..lol

so i saw my college boyy last night, we hung out, hooked up...i cant believe it tho cause i never thought id see him again..


hmm me nd friends are goin out tnight...we'll c what trouble we get into LOL

idk whats wrong w/ me...im like hyperventilating and like ready to have a heart attack...im soo weirdly antsy about a lot of things...

first off im like soooo underprepared for my organic chem and college chem exams on wednesday

and im like weirdly nervous about going up to amherst...i have no idea why...

eww im like having a panic attack

i guess plans have changed...i will be going up to amherst next wknd for a visit...this shall be interesting..

i wonder if i'll have any drama haha..

so anyways im going out with jonny tmrw..and im pretty excited about it...hes my new guy and im very interested...we talk all day everyday, and hes just funny 

so i think we're gonna go bowling or maybe out to eat again...we'll c

so i randomly decided to put my facebook back...

i was off facebook for almost 6 months, cause i just needed to focus on school and finishing my pre-reqs strong, with no distractions..


plus im not in college anymore, so its different...but i put it back and caught up w/ some ppl on it...interesting

but anyway i was thinkin of doing a reunion in ny or ma...i wanted to go up to amherst, but it doesnt seem like my friends are that open to it...i just sense that..and im not quite sure why

hmm oh well...anyway, im gonna get back to doing phys extra credit.

i broke my fast like a month ago tho...but im still celebrating anyway lol

im so hungryy i want a chipotle burrito! with my vodka-orange liqueur drink...but i dont wanna offend my mom cuz shes been cooking all day..

im just gonna go get my drink and chill...

just another day of waiting..this is torture..

on a positive note, im talking to a new guy, and im really interested in him

hes really funny, im a sucker for comedians lol

i guess i better get to my hw..

when will something good happen?? seriously.

i hate student loan companies! they have been harassing me even tho IM STILL A STUDENT!

eww i hate this whole deferment process its a nightmare

i wish i just had a million dollars to pay off my loans, put myself thru med school, and buy a house..

id be set.

ugh.

Baby baby
When we first met I never felt something so strong
You were like my lover and my best friend
All wrapped in one with a ribbon on it
And all of a sudden you went and left
I didn't know how to follow
It's like a shock that spun me around
And now my heart's dead
I feel so empty and hollow

And I'll never give myself to another the way I gave it to you
You don't even recognize the ways you hurt me, do you?
It's gonna take a miracle to bring me back
And you're the one to blame
And now I feel like....oh!

You're the reason why I'm thinking
I don't wanna smoke on these cigarettes no more
I guess that's what I get for wishful thinking
Should've never let you enter my door

Next time you wanna go on and leave
I should just let you go on and do it
'Cause now I'm using like I bleed

It's like I checked into rehab
And baby, you're my disease
It's like I checked into rehab
And baby, you're my disease
I gotta check into rehab
'Cause baby you're my disease
I gotta check into rehab
'Cause baby you're my disease

Damn, ain't it crazy when you're loveswept (?)
You'd do anything for the one you love
'Cause anytime that you needed me I'd be there
It's like you were my favorite drug
The only problem is that you was using me
In a different way than I was using you
But now that I know it's not meant to be
I gotta go, I gotta wean myself off of you

yay, i did well on my chem exams! i got a 98% and i was shocked...my prof said she was proud of me for showing so much improvement, cause i kinda struggled in the beginning of the semester...

and the med schools have been calling/emailing me...so hopefully thats a positive sign

we shall see..

ive been grooming myself all morning...doing my hair, eyebrows, maybe ill paint my nails a little later...i love grooming when i have the day to myself, it just relaxes me :)

and i need to take my mind off of some stuff..

still waiting on the schools...on the positive side i dont have any rejections, but also i havent been accepted yet...when i call to check with the schools they always say the same thing "your file is under review"..hmm

well i have a study group session at 1pm today...i have 2 tests tommorow in organic chem and college chem

so i need to learn how to NOT stress out about stuff...cause one of my biggest fears is aging lol

i dont wanna let stress take its toll on my youth..soo im gonna learn better coping mechanisms..i should probably learn to eat better too

im gonna go get some breakfast...

im doing some spring cleaning, finally!

MY ROOM HAS BEEN A MESS, just like my life! lol

My mom is having some guests over so i figured the least i could do was straighten up a bit...

maybe if my room is less cluttered, my mind will be too?
i dyed my hair. i now have burgandy highlights and i LOVE it! that is all..

im feelin sooo antsy..

im buzzed, and im tryin to control my drunken urges...tryin sooo hard not to drunk dial my love..i miss him soo much..he must have an allergy to me or something..he hasnt called me in a whileeeeeee

he must not care anymore.and it bothers me

plus im feelin down about the whole futuree thing...havent heard back from the med schools yet and im feelin ANTSYYYYY..

im so scared of what the future holds...eww i cant.

so, im gonna start looking at guys as science experiments...

theres gonna be an intro(how we met), a purpose(what he wants from me), a hypothesis (my prediction of whats gonna happen), a procedure (little step by step of the major stuff he does), an observation (self explanatory), and a discussion of results/conclusion (also self explanatory)...

lol

so lets start with lee..
intro (we met so randomly, in a parking lot lol)

purpose (i get the feeling he wants a gf, but im not sure if thats specifically me or if he just wants one in general)

hypothesis (i predict that we'll talk for a few weeks before we come to some sort of crossroads...i doubt it'll be a hook up thing...hes slightly intense so it'll either be a dating thing or just a friendship)

procedure(hmm hes very consistent with the calling...he called before, during, after my ft lauderdale trip, hes slightly jealous when i talk about other guys, ive cancelled 2 dates w/ him and he kept his cool, we've met up for starbucks & another time at the mall...so far sooo good)

observation (same as above)

conclusion (will come back to this one in a few weeks and see where we're at)

i just got back from a great date...i think im really starting to like this new guy....its such a strange feeling because i havent liked anyone new in soooooo long...

im happy :)

im allllll set with bad boys, from now on, only good guys :)

i had a pretty good day tday...

had orgo, chem, chem lab...then i went to dinner w. mark nd it was pretty fun! we had some interesting convos about sex and the city, and boys, and r/ps and stuff haha

i talked to lee...hes my new guy...we've been talkin for like 2 weeks now...hes very consistent which i like....

hes put up with my bs so far...i already backed out of 2 dates but hes still callin...so i like that...cause im very moody so i need someone who will deal w/ that...

so we'll see..

by may i think ill know about the med schools...til then im gonna apply to jobs cause i dont wanna be left hanging with no where to go and nothing to do...i have my job for now but im scared of the future.....hmm

so its spring break, officially! haha

but i have to work tommorow...booo...damn i wish spring break was like 3 weeks instead

im going to ft lauderdale in like 5 days and im damn excited, get it!!

gonna do some orgo hw problems, then im going shoppppppinnnngggggg<3333

havent done that in a while..i shouldnt be spending money cause of the economy n such, but i hardly ever get to shop anymore cause i never have time

ohhh well...im gonna buy some sundresses, already have some flip flops and sunglasses, maybe a few shirts? im gonna get my nails done on sunday or monday...doing my hair on tuesday o heyyyyy yayyy

i just need to find my damn camera tho!! yikesss

man, writing these secondaries is like pulling teeth....


im really grappling with this which is so strange, bc normally writing comes naturally to me


maybe cause i havent written an essay in a while?

all this chem/physics/bio/orgo has taken over my lifeeee haha :)

i need to get it together tho...

i have zero energy and motivation to write these secondaries...ew

where did the motivation go? the excitement? i was all anxious and ready....

now ive fallen off...dont really care anymore...not a good thing

so last night i got waaaasted....havent done that in forever!

i went on a double date...well it was sposed to be a double date...my date showed up and he was sposed to bring a friend for my friend but his friend got too drunk before he came lmao!

i was pretty drunk by the time we met up which is probably not a good idea...but i just had like 2 rum n cokes and a beer and i was already trashed

its so strange to have a low tolerance cause before that little amount of alcohol would never phase me and now its more than enough to get me drunk

and of course i got a little emotional...hence the 'poor me' post below :)

haha

and i got really emotional about my guy situation...i was like pouring my heart out to phyl about the way i feel about the guys ive talked to/dated in the past....she was probably like overwhelmed lol

and omg i was kinda bored with my date so i started like drawing chemical structures on the napkins at the bar...i was like texting other guys...eww im so rude...im not normally like that but i was just drunk..

haha it was kind of fun tho...but got a little emotional at the end....im so weird.

im an attention whore i know...i just wish someone cared about me.

:(

i hate guys.

yay my florida trip is coming up sooooon!! March 11-14!

i already told my boss im taking off from weds-saturday...

im so excited to go back to ft lauderdale...been to florida like 5 times...

been going like once a year cause its just therapeutic to me...the beach, the weather, the relaxationnn

and yayy im going with jessie! it'll be sooo fun cause we haven't seen each other in like, 3 yrs so we'll have fun...cant wait to drink and chill at the beach.

and get tons of rest...

my goal is to have ALL my applications completed so that when i go i won't have any responsibilities lingering in my mind..

hopefully i wont have a lot of homework that wknd or any tests...

actually i dont care, i REFUSE to think negatively during the trip and im not bringing any stress with me....woo hoo im ready to go RIGHT NOW!!

I got the Florida boo!

clearly i have a lot to learn about men

i need to wake up and realize that bad guys are just not right for me, and instead focus on the nice ones


no one can change anybody...and no one can especially change a bad guy


i need to be with the nice guy this time...im gonna hang with this guy on saturday...need to be with someone like him...need to GET OVER the bad guy...seriously

But something happened
For the very first time with you
My heart melted to the ground
Found something true
And everyone's looking 'round
Thinking I'm going crazy

Oooh, yahhh

But I don't care what they say
I'm in love with you
They try to pull me away
But they don't know the truth 

-leonnaaaa

im such a loser :P


hundreds of miles away and he was still my valentine <3


i couldnt help but to talk to him, it had been awhile, and i had to know how he felt about me


he said he missed me, asked if id come up to visit

i would but i dont know if its such a good idea..amherst is so far....but i miss him terribly...

yeah im a loser


but valentines day was fun! went out for sushi and drinks with my friends at this posh restaurant/lounge in dc...it was all valentines themed-red n white..very cute place...then we went to clydes in va...just chilled out...nd i got to talk to my valentine :)

but im back to being on the grind...i knocked out my physics homework this wknd, wrote my prelab and post lab for chem, taking my physics exam tommorow, filling out the FAFSA and then formulating a rough draft for my secondary apps for med school

i got 3 secondary invites so i have to finish those...then i need to finish my carib school apps too, send those out and get the ball rolling

damn i hope i get at least one interview...just one is all i need...please please please please GOD!

i have a bad feeling about this whole med school application thing..

i dont think im gonna get in


i wish i could be more optimistic. but i dont think its gonna happen


my undergrad grades werent that great.  damn i wish i could do it all over again.  unless i miraculously scored well on the mcat, i just dont know if i can pull it off.

the admissions committee would just have to be in one hell of a nice mood to accept me.

eww i need to work on my self esteem :(

just a little down today.......

so time is definitely flying by...its like the middle of february already...damn

just came back from the movies, i saw "slumdog millionaire", it really blew me away....amazing movie, truly

but back to the craziness...finished my orgo test, now gotta do some physics homework, take the exam and write the labs...............blahhhh i dont wanna do itttt!


its just an endless cycle. work. class. homework. labs. shadowing. test. applications. more class. more work. family time. 

wheres the ME time????

i feel like today was the first time i got to be a human being, and got a chance to go relax and watch a movie....but i have this looming fear that i should still be doing work for my classes...or be productive in some other way


im such a worrier. and a complainer. i really need to change that about myself. its a serious neurosis....and eww where did it come from because i used to be so laid back! 

ayy...i guess the adult world is not agreeing with me :(

my friends called me to go out for sushi and drinks on saturday...i agreed as long as i got a chance to finish my phys homework...damn my life always takes a backseat to my work but i guess i just have to keep this up til may 11th then ill be freeeeeeee!

well for a little bit at least :-)

when does it get easier?


i seriously feel like im sinking with every passing day...i have no motivation to study for my orgo test..not good..not good at all
boo i got a little nostalgic today...i kinda miss college :(

im so tired its not even funny......i literally am going to fall over one of these days


im sleep deprived, nervous, anxious, physically exhausted, emotionally drained..

i dont wanna haaaang out


i dont even remember the last time i did something fun 

work was hell today, i hate my job.....class was awful yesterday, im falling behind in orgo 2

im starving so im gonna go eat..fuck everything

i was just thinkin about the past and all...and i've realized something


in all my four years of college, i never met a single guy who was really worth dating..


i dont keep in touch with ANY of them, unless we were just friends...wow

i guess part of it is my own fault, because i probably didn't portray myself well, in the 'girlfriend' light or whatever....but mostly i was just figuring out who i am...it was my first time being on my own, with any kind of freedom, free of pressure from family to behave a certain way

but still, four years and nothing?

i dated a little here and there, but none of em were worth it

i met some good friends though, and i wouldn't trade my experiences for the world...now i don't plan to get serious or anything because i think that certain things are out of one's control, but i do want to put myself forward as more of an adult...because i truly do feel that im finally growing up...becoming the person i've wanted to be

focusing/planning my future...being self confident about what i have to offer (and not in the physical sense)

im happy now, but i still have a lot to work on.....i guess i won't ramble anymore, i should study some chem before i fall asleep :-P

after NOT thinkin about him for such a long time, i had a dream about him.........


why why why
